[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-plan-deviation flags                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Escalation history                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Storage architecture]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Structured data: DynamoDB tables                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation transcript: S3 with vector retrieval    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent-context summary: cached, refreshed per turn   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Episode-summary: refreshed on each material event    │
