[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    534[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    535[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Durable conversation record]                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    536[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - User utterances                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    537[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tool calls with arguments and results                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    538[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Generated bot responses                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    539[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active model and prompt versions                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    540[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active protocol corpus version                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    541[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active integration-contract versions                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    542[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Final disposition                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    543[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    544[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Coordination-decision-record journal]                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    545[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Durable, separately-governed record of coordination  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    546[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      events (escalations, care-plan-deviations, in-       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    547[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      network-verifications, prior-auth shepherding)       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    548[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Retention sized to the longer of HIPAA's six-year    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    549[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      minimum, state-specific medical-record retention,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    550[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and institutional regulatory floor                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    551[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    552[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Operational telemetry]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    553[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Engagement rate by patient cohort                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    554[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sibling-bot routing accuracy                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    555[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Citation-coverage rate                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    556[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Escalation rate by trigger type                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    557[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Handoff-acceptance rate by human coordinators        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    558[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-cohort metric slices                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    559[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    560[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Sampled clinical-quality review]                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    561[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Random sample plus targeted sample of escalations,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    562[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      handoffs, and low-confidence cases                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    563[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Reviewers (RNs, care coordinators, clinical          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    564[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      leadership) tag failure modes (out-of-scope, off-    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    565[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      protocol, escalation-miss, escalation-false-positive,│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    566[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      tone-failure, citation-gap, sibling-bot-routing-     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    567[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      error, frustration-handling-failure)                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    568[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Protocol revisions driven by review findings with    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    569[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      clinical-leadership sign-off                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    570[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
